## Few other services


### IRC stats

Though we do not keep a public log of the IRC channel, but we maintain a
statistics page for the channel. You can find it `here <http://dgplug.org/ircstat/>`_.

### Planet

We also maintain a planet with the blog feeds of dgplug.org members. To add your blog
to the planet, please contact any of the admins in the IRC channel.

### rfc.dgplug.org

We also have a `mirror of RFC texts  <http://rfc.dgplug.org>`_.

